Trip Overview

Immerse yourself in a 3-day cultural journey through Rome, featuring visits to world-famous museums, walks through the historic city center, and relaxing breaks in charming cafés. Highlights include a tour of the Vatican, the Colosseum, a hands-on pasta-making class, and much more.
